dct_title_s: Automobile road from San Francisco, Cal. to Vancouver, B.C. via Sacramento - Portland - Tacoma - Seattle - etc
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; A.J.B.
Relief shown by spot heights (cities only).
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Indicates distances from San Francisco and Vancouver.
Numbered 111 in lower left, 3 in upper right, and 68 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
